Description: CVE-2026-44170 - MDEV-39289 CONNECT REST support on Windows doesn't escape the url
 Use _spawnlp instead of CreateProcess so URL/args do not need shell escaping,
 preventing argument injection via crafted URLs in the CONNECT REST table type.
 Reported by Aisle Research.
Origin: upstream, https://github.com/MariaDB/server/commit/aca6743d5345ffa49a7c17db01734475cd3d2783
